c_t start_POSTSUBSCRIPT 0 end_POSTSUBSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math>=
 as well. An indivisible stochastic process does not, therefore,
need to violate logical time-reversal invariance in any fundamental
way.</p><button class=3D"sr-only button" style=3D"display: none;">Report is=
sue for preceding element</button>
</div>
