<div class=3D"ltx_para" id=3D"S3.SS2.p1">
<p class=3D"ltx_p">To make the nonuniqueness of the potential matrix <math =
alttext=3D"\Theta\mathopen{}\mathclose{{\left(t\leftarrow 0}}\right)" class=
