hclose{{\left(t\leftarrow 0}}\right)</annotation><annotation encoding=3D"ap=
plication/x-llamapun">roman_=CE=98 start_OPEN end_OPEN start_CLOSE ( italic=
_t =E2=86=90 0 end_CLOSE )</annotation></semantics></math>
more manifest, it will be helpful to introduce an analogy with the
Maxwell theory of classical electromagnetism.<span class=3D"ltx_note ltx_ro=
