=3D"application/x-llamapun">roman_=CE=A8 start_OPEN end_OPEN start_CLOSE ( =
italic_t end_CLOSE )</annotation></semantics></math> is available, the Born=
 rule (<a class=3D"ltx_ref" href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2507.21192v1#S3.=
E46" title=3D"In 3.4 The Hilbert-Space Representation =E2=80=A3 3 Review of=
 the Stochastic-Quantum Correspondence =E2=80=A3 Quantum Systems as Indivis=
ible Stochastic Processes"><span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_ref_tag">46</span></=
