\mathclose{{\left(t\leftarrow 0}}\right)" class=3D"ltx_math_unparsed" displ=
ay=3D"inline" id=3D"S3.SS5.p7.m3"><semantics><mrow><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi></mi=
><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=3D"false">=E2=86=90</mo><mn>0</mn><=
/mrow></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">U\=
mathopen{}\mathclose{{\left(t\leftarrow 0}}\right)</annotation><annotation =
encoding=3D"application/x-llamapun">italic_U start_OPEN end_OPEN start_CLOS=
E ( italic_t =E2=86=90 0 end_CLOSE )</annotation></semantics></math>
corresponds to making a gauge choice=E2=80=94or, somewhat more
precisely, to a partial fixing of the gauge freedom (<a class=3D"ltx_ref" h=
