</button>
</div>
<div class=3D"ltx_para" id=3D"S3.SS5.p8">
<p class=3D"ltx_p">If the unitary time-evolution operator <math alttext=3D"=
U\mathopen{}\mathclose{{\left(t\leftarrow 0}}\right)" class=3D"ltx_math_unp=
